<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Ищем близких</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/css/app.css") %>"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/css/materialize.min.css">

    <script defer type="text/javascript" src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/js/app.js") %>"></script>
</head>
<body>
<nav>
    <div class="nav-wrapper light-blue">
        <a href="#" class="brand-logo center" style="font-size:1.5rem" >Ищем близких</a>
    </div>
</nav>


<main role="main" class="container">
    <p class="alert alert-info" role="alert"><%= get_flash(@conn, :info) %></p>
    <p class="alert alert-danger" role="alert"><%= get_flash(@conn, :error) %></p>
    <%= @inner_content %>
</main>
<footer class="page-footer white">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12 m4 l2"></div>
            <div class="col s12 m4 l8">
                <p class="black-text text-lighten-4"><b>Последнее обновление в <%=" #{Timex.now("Europe/Minsk") |> Timex.format!("%H:%M:%S", :strftime)} " %></b></p>
                <p class="black-text text-lighten-4">Информация собрана волонтёрами канала <a href="https://t.me/spiski_okrestina" target="_blank" >@spiski_okrestina</a> из всех доступных источников.  </p>
                <p class="black-text text-lighten-4"><%= "В базе информация о #{@db_size} задержаниях с 01.10.2020" %>  </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col s12 m4 l2"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
